            <summary>Appointment by Giovanni de' Buondelmonti and his heirs on one side, and Francesco di Neri Fioravante and his heirs, weavers from Florence, on the other, of Bernardo and Gherardo di Bartolomeo Gherardi, Antonio and Vestro di Baldo, and Andrea di Chimente, all Florentine citizens, as mediators and judges in an unidentified dispute. Notarized by Ambrogio d'Angiolo Augini from Florence on 20 August 1418 and extracted from the records of notary Alberto di Russo. Filed with the document is a short, later summary written in Italian on paper.</summary>
